> You might want to take the same amount off the flange the bolts go through 
> between the flange &the ports. This way you won't create a real good exhaust 
> leak.
> 
> A trick is to put some blue oil paint on the tips of the pipes. Then file 
> till gone.
> Remember to take the same amount from the flanges where they meet the head.
